rows.name: Welcome to Army Pizza! You here for a pie?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085909_MSG0002
rows.name:
...Hmm? You need 10 delivered as soon as possible?
No sweat! For just 10,000 credits, we'll send your
piping-hot pizzas anywhere in New LA![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085909_JNK0010
rows.name: Purchase

rows.label: qev085909_SEL0011
rows.name: Buy the pizzas for 10,000 credits.

rows.label: qev085909_JNK0020
rows.name: Wait

rows.label: qev085909_SEL0021
rows.name: Hold off for now.

rows.label: qev085909_MSG0003
rows.name:
Thank you very much!
And these are headed to Jeshero's place, right?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085909_MSG0009
rows.name: We'll have 'em there before the cheese begins to cool![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085909_MSG0004
rows.name:
Hey, no problem. Come back any time you wanna
stop the sides of your belly from clanging together![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085909_MSG0011
rows.name: ...Uh-oh! Do you not have the money?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085909_MSG0012
rows.name: I'm really sorry, but we're cash only here.[ST:wait ]
